<p>Hi <%= @member.name %>,</p>

<p>
  Welcome to FreelyShared! You've successfully registered
  <strong><%= @church.name %></strong> as a sharing community.
</p>

<p>
  <strong>Next step:</strong> invite your church members to join! Share the link
  below with your congregation — at church, in your group chat, newsletter, or
  on the noticeboard:
</p>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
  <a href="<%= @join_url %>" class="btn">Join <%= @church.name %></a>
</p>

<p style="text-align: center; color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px;">
  Or share this link directly:<br>
  <a href="<%= @join_url %>"><%= @join_url %></a>
</p>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
  <strong>Scan to join:</strong><br>
  <img src="<%= @qr_url %>" alt="QR code to join <%= @church.name %>" width="200" height="200" style="margin-top: 12px; border-radius: 8px;">
</p>

<p style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 14px;">
  <strong>Tip:</strong> Print the QR code above and put it on your church noticeboard
  or include it in your weekly bulletin. People can scan it with their phone camera
  to go straight to the sign-up page.
</p>

<% if @church.members_needed > 0 %>
<p>
  Your church needs <strong><%= @church.members_needed %> more members</strong> to
  activate. Once you reach 5 members, everyone will be notified and the sharing
  platform will go live!
</p>
<% end %>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; color: #6c757d;">
  <em>"All the believers were one in heart and mind. No one claimed that any of their
  possessions was their own, but they shared everything they had."</em><br>
  <strong>— Acts 4:32</strong>
</p>
